{"tid":2223560,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 超級機器人大戰DD [33] Change! Noir G! Swicth On!","createTime":"2020-09-30T02:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:23:36.000Z","uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb588c2b684931fd76f826353b6c9e9f561cf0a","tid":2223560,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">前言：<br />\n此遊戲營運曾無理凍結大量玩家賬號<br />\n到時出現退錢及棄驚潮<br />\n此驚就執 有興趣的玩家請勿課金</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">重有心玩嘅可以睇#1 有齊資料,傷害計算器同埋好友表 就算巴打被ban你都可以Add嚟抱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://srw-dd-tw.suparobo.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsrw-dd-tw.suparobo.jp&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e1ead0dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://srw-dd-tw.suparobo.jp</a><br />\n官方wiki : <a href=\"https://wiki.dengekionline.com/srwdd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.dengekionline.com%2Fsrwdd%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e0c9d9d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.dengekionline.com/srwdd/</a><br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n1. 點解壓制戰咁難打, 我升滿GGG都比人秒?<br />\nA: 壓制戰要再裝一次啲卡<br />\n<br />\n2. 我行路就斷CHAIN點解成就?<br />\nA: AUTO就唔斷<br />\n<br />\n真三一要點攞?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjUYOTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjUYOTT.jpg&h=913f7846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 鎚仔打Extra Stage有冇分類? <br />\nA : <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhjLtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhjLtd.jpg&h=621104ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPilot 訓練書可以鳩分3類 唔同類食唔同書 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DFURoN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDFURoN2.jpg&h=659d18d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n出擊夠10-1000場數會送唔同等級嘅書<br />\n [10-500場] <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bM5pWow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbM5pWow.jpg&h=ce8356a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n [520-1000場] <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pfp6Fvh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfp6Fvh.jpg&h=2b250cdb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">機體及支援類型分類 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.dengekionline.com/srwdd/機体タイプ一覧表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.dengekionline.com%2Fsrwdd%2F%E6%A9%9F%E4%BD%93%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E8%A1%A8&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=de8084e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.dengekionline.com/srwdd/機体タイプ一覧表</a><br />\n<br />\n好友登記<br />\n日版巴打<br />\n1.燥底新丁 138325931 シオン・ザバ<br />\n2.チンポ 120954382 すず<br />\n3.強迫症 156260136 M<br />\n4.松岡茉優BB 373316501 マイルス<br />\n5.食蜜瓜先 635813533 Ray Lihk<br />\n6.米田共人 176069017 アムロ<br />\n7.雞巴忠實粉絲 395935139 JK<br />\n8.茂吉 348878457 茂吉<br />\n9. 禿髮樹機能 273703387 なまにく<br />\n<br />\n港版巴打<br />\n1. zeta 171208454 zeta<br />\n2.李智恩 164812904 阿榮<br />\n3.死侍 270525800 社會主義鐵拳<br />\n4.星乜尻卡樂D 261818312 快d出dann<br />\n5.～敵退我追～ 174742386 廢雀爺 &amp; 159823188 費爵爺<br />\n6.銀時 175838625 安妮亞<br />\n7.齒輪 162866713 HIM<br />\n8. ※葵※ 182976353 香港人‧葵‧報仇<br />\n9. 基爾禾 293104131 真三一 +5<br />\n10. 我愛aimyon 255540915 aimyon<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">機體總數值 及 輸出 &amp; 武器種類分類表,傷害計算器,好友表</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1E58vCSfQt2ot6qucNmkK0hnYikjAOuvKBwiw3K__VaI/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1E58vCSfQt2ot6qucNmkK0hnYikjAOuvKBwiw3K__VaI%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=bd19f120\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1E58vCSfQt2ot6qucNmkK0hnYikjAOuvKBwiw3K__VaI/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>綾波麗打手 卡樂D推介</strong><br />\n係呀男主依家可以硬到鋤地呀<br />\n但你敢唔敢講你呢部男主 用同樣配置 喺一年之後仲硬過彊屍呀<br />\n我見到呢隻驚戰力澎漲到痴線 下年d boss都可能有40000攻嘅可能性 <br />\n但你抽到新卡 特性滿就頂到囉<br />\n抽唔到新卡 練度唔高咁點呀<br />\n<br />\n我就係好撚憎跟住營運俾嘅路行 無限性buff高自己防禦<br />\n然後下一次冇石抽新卡 又唔夠力防 咁就仆直<br />\n<br />\n係呀大家依家用得好爽 我部男主都有萬四防<br />\n但鎮四呢？鎮五呢？唔通又臨打嗰陣先屌曬鬼 然後又扮坐定粒六 等中四技五技六技之後 猛咁讚嗰啲用得半年/一年課仔嘅技？<br />\n<br />\n我想玩減傷坦 係因為佢到依家仲保緊值 可以由鎮1打到Ex 30 而仲未有方法打壓佢住 <br />\n各位課長 我明你哋手上有好多卡拆 好多卡玩<br />\n保值呢家嘢對你哋嚟講可唔重要<br />\n但我 作為睇咗red同drecom柒足一年又唔想益佢班仆街嘅無課仔 係深感明白每一次賭資源升卡嘅重要性<br />\n我都知減傷坦 只要俾官方改一改公式 就即刻收皮<br />\n但我玩咗咁耐 淨係見到0號一技+4防傷sup 係保值過所有閃坦技/sup 同好多舊嘅攻防技 起碼唔使不斷擔心白值跟唔上<br />\n呢個就係我寧願儲資源玩減傷嘅原因"},{"pid":"28931d68a5be80df726cbc92deb1f5d09ee9763f","tid":2223560,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"手快串錯SWITCH字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fa8ed3e06c1b0641177aa6571f4a1852a16427","tid":2223560,"uid":60083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28931d68a5be80df726cbc92deb1f5d09ee9763f","tid":2223560,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"手快串錯SWITCH字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"開多個新post"},{"pid":"7f316efda1b4a6f8e7b70d7f28cf8a2df5e63b64","tid":2223560,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6fa8ed3e06c1b0641177aa6571f4a1852a16427","tid":2223560,"uid":60083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28931d68a5be80df726cbc92deb1f5d09ee9763f","tid":2223560,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"手快串錯SWITCH字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"開多個新post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"12410f804d7ba835a3bd8dceff4a10389b3535cb","tid":2223560,"uid":6635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"三一機械人大戰<img src=\"/assets/